Say '''Albuera''' et kumatlo ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Leyte]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 40,553 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 303.35 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumapat ya distrito. Say zip code to et 6542.	
															
